{"tid":1825480,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"點解落選區議員仲可以係度阻住地球轉？追擊大圍民賤聯肥西","createTime":"2020-01-15T10:08:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T16:23:04.000Z","uid":308392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f31be968f7faa9ae7f4c6af0f653694efedb29dc","tid":1825480,"uid":308392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T10:08:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YKtUhBd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYKtUhBd.jpg&h=cef7a4a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n是咁的<br />\n我果區個落選<strong><ins>民賤聯</ins></strong>區議員<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">落選</span></strong>咗之後仲不斷<strong>sip宣傳單張</strong>落屋邨信箱 又時不時send埋啲咁嘅嘢黎 個議員辦事處一路都無諗住搬走 仲改埋個名比自己：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">社區服務主任</span></strong><br />\n條友仲要落選左之後仲要<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">周圍掛banner</span></span></strong>話自己做左幾多嘢<br />\n好撚煩呀唔想再比落選區議員滋擾 可以點做？<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EZKkdci.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEZKkdci.png&h=9eaed474&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1119d466b95354fd55f79dbf57d605aa940d35ed","tid":1825480,"uid":92,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T10:15:35.000Z","msg":"樓主自爆左啊 收返個嬲啦"},{"pid":"9196f7af95f650f3c30bfafd097d34d7a48af046","tid":1825480,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T10:24:10.000Z","msg":"Hi"},{"pid":"708835232a98da861451669837cc329754a00036","tid":1825480,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1119d466b95354fd55f79dbf57d605aa940d35ed","tid":1825480,"uid":92,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T10:15:35.000Z","msg":"樓主自爆左啊 收返個嬲啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T10:26:06.000Z","msg":"個個都入去比嬲咪得囉"},{"pid":"b709d563dc7860eb76cfe01f89c4567bc993b10a","tid":1825480,"uid":44298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T10:26:13.000Z","msg":"佢喺民建聯創黨成員個女，有後台㗎。之前個個都話如何佢選到區議